{"tid":398953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"飛彈營突擊演習　解手軍正在聽音樂 錯過防空警報","createTime":"2017-09-13T14:31:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T14:44:34.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d5090ee9d6fbbc1a48c0cf8d233f2caa0618a0cc","tid":398953,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:31:13.000Z","msg":"陸媒：士兵演習聽音樂&ensp;致作戰失敗<br />\n2017/09/12<br />\n記者郜敏／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n　大陸官媒日前刊登1篇有關共軍某部隊實戰演習的報導，指共軍士兵因戴著耳機聽音樂錯過防空警報，導致作戰失敗，引發熱議。<br />\n<br />\n&emsp;評論指出，繼東部戰區陸軍第72集團軍某砲兵旅副旅長在演習中車禍死亡後，共軍又在演習中暴露了致命的缺點，共軍官兵戰備警戒素質低，令民眾質疑共軍戰力；另外也有評論指出，共軍從上到下的腐敗，若打起仗來，非常有可能全軍覆沒。<br />\n<br />\n　報導指出，8月23日晚間，北部戰區空軍地對空飛彈某營進入例行的小週末，士兵們開始洗衣服、打球或聽音樂，到了20時左右，營區突然響起防空警報，雖然大多數士兵立刻回到戰鬥崗位，但電源班班長和配電員未到位，連長只好讓另2位士兵頂替，但因替補的士兵操作不熟練，導致裝備當機，最終該連在這場突擊演習中失敗。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ydn.com.tw/News/253819\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ydn.com.tw%2FNews%2F253819&d=E9yJEMmn1VVTMm8ooIaxqywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=d883f157\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ydn.com.tw/News/253819</a>"},{"pid":"314ce0d64cd3a7c6cc1a7f88a650642f5001ca40","tid":398953,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:32:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陸媒：士兵演習聽音樂&ensp;致作戰失敗<br />\n2017/09/12<br />\n記者郜敏／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n　大陸官媒日前刊登1篇有關共軍某部隊實戰演習的報導，指共軍士兵因戴著耳機聽音樂錯過防空警報，導致作戰失敗，引發熱議。<br />\n<br />\n&emsp;評論指出，繼東部戰區陸軍第72集團軍某砲兵旅副旅長在演習中車禍死亡後，共軍又在演習中暴露了致命的缺點，共軍官兵戰備警戒素質低，令民眾質疑共軍戰力；另外也有評論指出，共軍從上到下的腐敗，若打起仗來，<span style=\"color: red;\">非常有可能全軍覆沒</span>。<br />\n<br />\n　報導指出，8月23日晚間，北部戰區空軍地對空飛彈某營進入例行的小週末，士兵們開始洗衣服、打球或聽音樂，到了20時左右，營區突然響起防空警報，雖然大多數士兵立刻回到戰鬥崗位，但電源班班長和配電員未到位，連長只好讓另2位士兵頂替，但因替補的士兵操作不熟練，導致裝備當機，最終該連在這場突擊演習中失敗。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ydn.com.tw/News/253819\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ydn.com.tw%2FNews%2F253819&d=E9yJEMmn1VVTMm8ooIaxqywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=d883f157\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ydn.com.tw/News/253819</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又唔會<br />\n<br />\n因為到時佢地已經走哂佬or投哂降"},{"pid":"eee95b6b61beb4f2746197adb22ccafd8d946dcf","tid":398953,"uid":17081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:33:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e14ac3a35d2b09a46eb243c74897fbfef00879d","tid":398953,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:34:53.000Z","msg":"國共兩軍都係咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73b233568725f54e83b6b764ea23a42874109ead","tid":398953,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:39:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國共兩軍都係咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打自己人民 果陣就會戰鬥力上升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fcdaa30e831137b3b5b9a51571ba873a698b0ed","tid":398953,"uid":47674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:41:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://image.soogif.com/8XcUrHQj4lKTcWO43sAA0lbZJwd1u1H5.gif_s400x0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.soogif.com%2F8XcUrHQj4lKTcWO43sAA0lbZJwd1u1H5.gif_s400x0&h=21123119&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6747e1f2118f4a5224ef0c45a3b38ad3a1499e54","tid":398953,"uid":120908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:41:54.000Z","msg":"洗撚人打咩，禁制發炮姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f420c5f841968f95914340dcc6cd3ec36f300a0a","tid":398953,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:44:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://image.soogif.com/8XcUrHQj4lKTcWO43sAA0lbZJwd1u1H5.gif_s400x0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.